HEADWORD: Self-posited
<hw>Self`-pos"it*ed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Disposed or
arranged by an action originating in one's self or in itself.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>These molecular blocks of salt are <qex>self-posited</qex>.</q>
